    'app.log_mgmt_91': 'Log Management (VCF 9.1) — Aria Operations for Logs 8.18 integrated in VCF Management Services. 1 FQDN required (lowercase) — e.g.: log-mgmt.vcf.domain.local (LB endpoint). 6 base IPs + 2 IPs per additional replica, all allocated from the VCF Services Runtime block (CIDR 198.18.0.0/15) — no additional IP. Day-N — deployed via VCF Operations Build.',
    'app.auto_91': 'VCF Automation (9.1) — 1 dedicated FQDN required (lowercase) — e.g.: automation.vcf.domain.local. User endpoint (= VIP). Cloud-native application in Services Runtime. + 1 dedicated VCF Services Runtime FQDN for Automation. /29 (5 IPs) block allocated on the network: 3 IPs assigned to nodes + 2 buffer IPs (redeploy/rolling updates) — nodes without individual DNS. Block independent from the Services Runtime block used by Fleet/Instance/Identity Broker; defaults to the Management VM Network, dedicated VLAN possible via the fleet lifecycle API.',
    'app.ib_embedded': 'Embedded in vCenter — lab/POC only. No dedicated IP. Not recommended in production.',
